See how teams from all over the globe work together to protect our most at-risk creatures on the new documentary #Endangered, narrated and produced by Ellen DeGeneres (@theellenshow). Stream now on @discoveryplus.  #EarthDay #EarthMonth

node.text:
Did you know sharks have two ears, just like humans? They’re located on either side of their head behind their eyes. But the question is - do they like rock n’ roll? 🎸

Head to our Instagram stories as @draustingallagher takes us on a field trip to Nassau, Bahamas where he takes us behind the scenes of the filming of Brad Paisley’s Shark Country. #sharkweek 

You can stream the show now on @discoveryplus: links.discoveryplus.com/bradpaisley

node.text:
The scalloped hammerhead shark uses its head to pin stingrays to the ocean floor, a vital skill for catching difficult-to-capture species. 🍴

Don't miss #SharkWeek tonight on Discovery and @discoveryplus! 

Kicking off the night at 8p ET is Ninja Sharks 2: Mutants Rising, followed by Monster Sharks of Andros Island and Mystery of the Black Demon Shark. 🏝

In for a jaw-dropping story? Continue the adrenaline with I Was Prey: Terrors from the Deep 2 at 11p ET. 

Stream Extinct or Alive: Jaws of Alaska on @discoveryplus. 🌟

Link in bio.

📸: Gerard Soury
